{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE. -->

=== Usage ===
<code>{{tlx|Lacking overview|2{{=}}specification of what should be summarized|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}</code>

The following will show up on the page:

{{Lacking overview|{{{1|article}}}|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}

This template will categorise tagged articles into [[:Category:Articles with sections that need to be turned into prose]] and [[:Category:Articles needing cleanup]].

== Redirects ==
* {{tl|Lacking outline}}
* {{tl|Lackingoutline}}
* {{tl|Lackingoverview}}
* {{tl|No outline}}
* {{tl|No overview}}
* {{tl|Nooutline}}
* {{tl|Nooverview}}

=== See also ===
* [[Template:Prose]]

